<lb n="0211c21"/><p>若比丘尼著<note n="0211007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">裨＝卑【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0211007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">裨＝卑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0211007"><lem>裨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">卑</rdg></app>身衣。波逸提</p><p type="inline">若比丘尼畜
