<lb n="0212a28"/>作二歲學戒羯磨竟。經宿乃授<note n="0212001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝具【明】</note><app n="0212001"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">具</rdg></app>學戒。波逸
<lb n="0212a29"/>提</p><p type="inline">若比丘尼自織作衣著。波逸提</p><p type="inline">若比
